public abstract class Algorithm
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

This class implements a bunch of helper methods that can be used in the method run() that should be implemented when this class is extended.

The current time. This is typically incremented in run().

currentMarkings

protected java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> currentMarkings
The current markings of the places in the StochasticPetriNet, i.e. the places is the reactants and the products of the reactions in the StochasticPetriNet.

run

public void run()
This method will initiate the algorithm run. This is the only method that needs to be overridden in order to implement a new algorithm.
